.;Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: The BJBC evaluation collected data from several sources, including an employment information system, site visits, a survey of frontline supervisors, a survey of clinical managers, and this survey of DCWs. The survey of frontline supervisors was released as ICPSR 23000: EVALUATION OF BETTER JOBS, BETTER CARE: FRONTLINE SUPERVISOR SURVEY, 2005-2007 [IOWA, NORTH CAROLINA, OREGON, PENNSYLVANIA, VERMONT]; and the survey of clinical managers was released as ICPSR 29063: EVALUATION OF BETTER JOBS BETTER CARE: CLINICAL MANAGER SURVEY, 2004-2007 [IOWA, NORTH CAROLINA, OREGON, PENNSYLVANIA, VERMONT].; Subject: null  Type: null  Notes: sav Data file(s), Data file(s), and electronic documentation.;
